Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mișcă sau te calc în picioare!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.99,0:00:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu! Nu te apropia!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oameni care mănâncă alți oameni?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.29,0:00:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce glumă îngrozitoare.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.48,0:00:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta nu este adevărat. \NEste imposibil să fie adevărat.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa, mami? Am dreptate?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unde te duci, Takagi?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce, aveai altceva de făcut?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.25,0:00:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Păi, mă gândeam să merg în cancelarie...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta este stupid.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce crezi că ar putea face profesorii noștri?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar, Takagi...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.13,0:00:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În această...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În această situație...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.62,0:00:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am o întrebare.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.89,0:00:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vrei să mori? Sau vrei să trăiești?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Păi, ei bine...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Privește. Acolo, la ușa cancelariei, sunt câteva persoane care au avut aceeași idee ca și tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Profesore!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Profesore!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu vreau să trăiesc!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai înțeles?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mișcă, fund gras!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.97,0:01:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.46,0:01:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takashi, te implor...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.88,0:01:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vreau să mor fiind eu însumi.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.18,0:01:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu se va...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.56,0:01:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu se va transforma în unul din ei!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oprește-te!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.82,0:02:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, vreau să știu ce \Nse întâmplă cu adevărat.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta a fost foarte direct.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce aș minți?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.91,0:02:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi poți împrumuta puțin telefonul? Vreau să încerc să-l sun pe tata.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.10,0:02:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știu că este polițist, dar cum îl vei contacta \Ncând linia de urgența a poliției este ocupată?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.12,0:02:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-a lăsat un număr privat pe care nu ar trebui să-l folosesc în mod normal.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sună!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.77,0:02:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alo?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acest număr de telefonul \Neste... al lui Takashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.36,0:02:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată, ascultă. Suntem la \Nșcoală în acest moment...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Alo? Takashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probabil ai acest număr de la Rei.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ea este bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Semnalul meu...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată?! Nu mă poți auzi?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ascultă, întregul oraș este \Nîntr-o stare de panică.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tată? Tată!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.00,0:02:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voi trebuie să—
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Întregul oraș este \Nîntr-o stare de panică!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să plecați cât mai repede—
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fără semnal?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar tocmai ce sunase!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De ce?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takashi...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tata...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.18,0:03:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nici măcar nu m-a recunoscut...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.33,0:03:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Takagi, ai cumva telefonul la tine? Este împotriva regulilor, dar—
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt o elevă de onoare!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.44,0:03:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiar dacă l-aș avea, pe cine aș suna?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Păi, ei bine, la poliție...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu chiar ești prost.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Privește cât de tare s-a înrâutățit situația.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu crezi că a încercat \Ncineva deja să sune la poliție?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.24,0:03:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu am auzit nicio sirenă până acum, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțelegi acum?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Întregul oraș este în haos?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.88,0:03:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probabil.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poliția a fost trimisă deja, probabil.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar uită-te la acest loc...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să sunăm la... \NForțele Apărării Naționale?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu aș conta nici pe ei.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știu că fără ordine de la guvern,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.65,0:04:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ei nu pot fi trimiși pentru apărare sau securitate public, dar—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mă refer la asta!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atunci, ce încerci—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt în aceeași situație ca și poliția.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.80,0:04:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide să presupunem că oamenii din toată Japonia se mănâncă reciproc. Ce crezi că se întâmplă?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ascultă, sunt 130 de milioane \Nde oameni în Japonia.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.31,0:04:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Din cei 130 de milioane, câți crezi \Ncă sunt în Forțele Apărării Naționale?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.30,0:04:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În plus, cine zice că cei din Forțele Apărării Naționale nu au fost afectați de asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide să ieșim de aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bine!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of, sunt blocată cu acest fund \Ngras deoarece Komuro a fugit.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.33,0:04:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cât de enervant.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okada...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okada?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La naiba!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.48,0:05:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău! Îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce ar trebui să fac?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.99,Dialogue Overlap,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău! Îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.84,Dialogue Overlap,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău! Îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi pare rău!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu reușesc să sun la \Npoliție sau la pompieri.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aș putea trata oamenii, dar odată \Nce au fost mușcați sunt ca și morți
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și revin la viața după ce mor.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.89,0:05:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă simt de parcă sunt într-unul din acele filme care le plac ciudaților.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este chiar așa impresionant?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haideți să mergem, asistentă Shizuka!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai o secundă.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să iau tot ce pot căra.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă rog să vă grăbiți!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asistentă Shizuka!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asistentă Shizuka!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fugiți! Repede!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine... Cum ai spus că te chema?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poftim?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hei...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Busujima Saeko, \Ncăpitanul Clubului de Kendo.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spune-mi, elev din \Nanul 2, cum te cheamă?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishii... Kazu...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai luptat vitejește ca s-o protejezi pe doctorița Marikawa, Ishii.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Curajul tău merită lăudat.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.49,0:06:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știi ce ți se întâmplă odată \Nce ai fost mușcat, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vrei ca părinții sau prietenii \Ntăi să te vadă așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă nu vrei asta,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,atunci îți voi pune eu \Ncapăt vieții aici și acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Totuși, va fi prima oară când omor un om.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.15,0:06:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Te rog...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stai o secundă, ce—
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știu că sunteți asistenta școlii, dar vă rog să nu interveniți.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.61,0:07:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Una din datoriile unei femei este să apere mândria unui bărbat.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.33,0:07:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce vom face acum că am ajuns aici, Takagi?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unele lucruri arată folositoare, dar—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ține-ți gura, gras ciudat.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Închide ușa ca să nu poată intra aici!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Am închis-o!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vom folosi astea ca arme?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.65,0:07:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu ești unul din acei ciudați căruia îi plac armele și armata, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.17,0:07:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ai văzut vreun film de acțiune cu unul din aceste lucruri?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Un pistol pentru cuie?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funcționează pe gaz?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normal!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ai putea să-l cari dacă ar avea un \Ncompresor ca cele din filme, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamne, ești așa prost.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți plac filmele?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu fi prost!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt un geniu care le știe pe toate!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mai avem un tub de gaz și câteva cuie.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu avem pentru ce să ne facem griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cum am putea să nu ne facem griji?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei vin!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vor intra prin hol!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cred că are cam 4 kilograme.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La fel ca o armă de asalt mai veche.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my stance will be messed up. It needs a sight.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, mă ignori?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirano?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te-am prins!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirano?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn it on!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.01,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw crap.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.84,0:09:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you put the drill and nails over there in a bag?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who gave you of all people the right to order me around?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please~?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oookay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.44,0:09:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sound happy to see us.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all feel great, don't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing? You should carry something, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Takagi... Mind if I ask you something?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Erm, why me?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No reason in particular.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the sudden mood swing?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to a realization?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know yet I do know!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirano!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes'm!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.43,0:10:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta hand it to you. It was a good idea to use the fire hose.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the water pressure is so strong.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.34,0:10:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember when we were in middle school and we had that fire drill and you and Hisashi...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to remember it this time.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'm ready to go now.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be rough in there. You sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Home.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.66,0:11:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll head to our houses and help survivors along the way.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.16,0:11:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our hometown. We should be able to feel our way around.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know my dad is safe, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.91,0:11:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you should call your house soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will sooner or later.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dad lives away from home because of his job,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:51.13,0:11:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and my mom is an elementary school\Nteacher so she wouldn't be at home either.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They probably wouldn't shut up if I got a hold of them anyway.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, we shouldn't be laughing right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.56,0:12:08.20,Emo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}I wasn't being serious about that, of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.90,Emo,,0,0,0,,When I looked at how things were at my own school,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.90,0:12:17.13,Emo,,0,0,0,,it frightened me to think of what it was like at my mom's school.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.09,0:12:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See how he didn't react when that rag hit him?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't feel pain so they only react to sound.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.03,0:12:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think they can see or he\Nwouldn't have run into that locker.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about, say, heat?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.59,0:12:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll try it if we have to.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we really gonna go outside?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.29,0:13:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, I don't like walking...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate fat nerds!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.49,0:13:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear you complain about\Nwalking until you're old enough to drive!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The staff room? What a difficult request you have made.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.54,0:13:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But everyone keeps their car keys in there...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.20,0:13:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you just kill them? It should be easy for you...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.65,0:13:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stopping to crush the head of everything we come across
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would be no different than\Nrestricting ourselves from movement.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would become surrounded.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.42,0:13:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be hard for us to get away should one of them take hold.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you really thought about this.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.63,0:13:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh jeez! What was that?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such fashion is unsuitable for running.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a brand name skirt!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.17,0:14:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, which do you value more? Your clothing or your life?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...both!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that from the staff room?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.15,0:14:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to figure out more of their traits if you keep killing them!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me fight them, Takagi!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do I have to fight?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.75,0:14:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm almost out of ammo!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.02,0:14:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?! Just reload it!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... behind you...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hirano!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm out!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare come near me!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.69,0:15:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go away...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.96,0:15:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,GO AWAY!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of these things!{ I want my mom! um..}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will take the right!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I got the left!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Takagi?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miyamoto...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are all acquainted with the\Nschool nurse, Ms. Marikawa, yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Saeko Busujima of 3-A.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Takashi Komuro from 2-B.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the same Busujima-{\i1}sempai{\i0} who won at the national championship last year?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in the Sojutsu Club. My name is Rei Miyamoto.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.47,0:16:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm, uhm, Kohta Hirano from B.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet all of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the... You're all so soft.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Sempai{\i0\fscx50} {\r}"? Seriously?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.67,0:17:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two are the same age! You must not know how to count since you got held back a year!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, Takagi...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like I'm stupid!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a genius!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can do anything once I put my mind to it!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.35,0:17:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.54,0:17:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is quite enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at how dirty I am...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to tell Mom to get it cleaned...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think it'll hold?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe we are all exhausted.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us rest here for a short while.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Takagi?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Glasses?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about them?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My contacts kept falling out!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glasses~
Dialogue: 100,0:20:23.61,0:20:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Takashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are your car keys, Ms. Marikawa?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.96,0:20:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're in my bag.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:32.87,0:20:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is your vehicle spacious\Nenough to seat all of us?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.01,0:20:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.85,0:20:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What of the miniature buses used for club\Nactivities? The keys hang from the wall in here.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That should work, but where are we going?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To check on our families.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll stop by everyone's home going from closest to furthest.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if we have to, we'll help our families too.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.86,0:20:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once we're done, we'll find a safe place to stay.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.26,0:21:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Rei?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:08.41,0:21:19.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,...government has started to do something about this on-going revolt. However, the politicians...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.69,0:21:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Revolt? They're calling this a revolt?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.74,0:21:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of deaths in the Saitama prefecture already exceeds 10,000.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prefectural governor has\Ndeclared a state of emergency—
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.13,0:21:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was gunfire!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, the police opened gunfire!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what are they shooting at?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:33.26,0:21:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Stay away!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:55.75,0:21:56.97,Preview - 1,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.68,Preview - 1,,0,0,0,,Let us act as a team.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.66,0:21:57.94,Preview - 2,,0,0,0,,Let's move!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.96,Preview - 2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, the same disease that has infected people here is spreading throughout the world.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.96,Preview - 1,,0,0,0,,This world is done for.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:00.96,0:22:01.75,Preview - 2,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.04,Preview - 1,,0,0,0,,I said RUN!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.05,Preview - 1,,0,0,0,,We should leave him to die!
