Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:29.97,ED01,,0,0,0,,aka ni nureru hoo no mukishitsu ga kanjou wo kuruwaseru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:43.99,ED01,,0,0,0,,dakara zutto boku no soba ni ite zutto mimamotteite
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:56.78,ED01,,0,0,0,,fukai yami ni karada wo uzumete ima wa subete wo wasure yo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:09.48,ED01,,0,0,0,,hageshii koe ga kokoro wo iyashite yami wo tatsukara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:23.99,ED01,,0,0,0,,hikari no naka dakarete nemuru tenshi no youna yokogao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:30.61,ED01,,0,0,0,,kodoku wo shitta bokutachi wa tada
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:37.09,ED01,,0,0,0,,sugaritakatta dake nano kana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:29.97,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,My inhuman cheek, wet with red, drives me nuts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:43.99,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,Stay by my side forever, always watching over me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:56.78,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,Now I forget it all as my body gets buried in the vile darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:19:09.48,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,Your fiery voice fights the darkness and heals my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:23.99,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,Your face is like that of an angel sleeping snugly in the light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:30.61,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,Those of us who came to know loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:37.09,ED01 TL,,0,0,0,,just want to know if we can depend on it alone
